This page provides support and contact information for the BTHome Sensors mobile application.

Contact

If you have questions, issues, or feedback, contact the developer:

Email: bthome.sensors@gmail.com

Common questions

  • The app scans nearby Bluetooth devices using the BTHome protocol.
  • Sensor data is stored locally on your device only.
  • You can delete stored data at any time from within the app.
  • Bluetooth and Location permissions are required for device scanning.
